ne more sec, forever you'll be here<br />\n記載印證我們的傳記<br />\nWe will leave the world behind, tonight<br />\n<br />\n終於走到這日這地 <br />\n繪的花撒盡了各地<br />\n起點寫滿某人某事 回味"},{"pid":"2568d77ea182e16c437fcd59a69c1c18f680f402","tid":2418582,"uid":375317,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"fc750808b8a090c6f409b21190afc0238bccbc9a","tid":2418582,"uid":211578,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"曲詞編監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:20:45.000Z","msg":"真心有料"},{"pid":"fd458f0f8f3df89ec52ccfa320ebd4eb067beed8","tid":2418582,"uid":68722,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02950c0c998e76807ccdf4049a0332308c9fc48c","tid":2418582,"uid":127454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:22:51.000Z","msg":"自己po自己上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb38d154428d4c063e78090fa92a877b6f37c84","tid":2418582,"uid":190432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T23:32:05.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪Eagle嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510e0b83b58a6025e070206cedff92ce6f00ede7","tid":2418582,"uid":26001,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:38:57.000Z","msg":"鷹之愛者 + 會員編號<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 支持"},{"pid":"8dcd42e4527e900cac80d8c3ec1561156b765e83","tid":2418582,"uid":320487,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T22:17:50.000Z","msg":"Eagle 做咩同aiden Justin June 反面呀