哋好似舊年9月左右就冇乜互動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁可惜 覺得佢哋一齊夾歌好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係最近先睇造星2同埋留意eagle<br />\n都覺得奇怪點解b4好似講咗一排話出道 但最後都好似冇聲氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47714da5b07b11a35bd204e8b28c1421e62382fc","tid":2418582,"uid":31359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3c248fa0df43238c514ab774d5c0a6596d7a1ea5","tid":2418582,"uid":190432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3922854867f8c0623b52a4c994d93c7fcd17b4a2","tid":2418582,"uid":320487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d637cfddd404acecdf864329671393e4d0e7631a","tid":2418582,"uid":190432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T18:55:06.000Z","msg":"Eagle到底為乜要同佢哋反面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T18:55:52.000Z","msg":"我都想知 <br />\nJune justin 開live 冇講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T19:07:10.000Z","msg":"我記得佢哋個live有講過 有人喺佢哋度take advantage<br />\n睇嚟似係講緊Eagle<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nEagle點解會變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:06:34.000Z","msg":"Eagle 係好撚假 大學嘅時候識佢<br />\n簡單啲講佢就係嗰啲好鍾意利用人 然後自己付出最少 但又要扮到好落力嗰種<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道你上面講佢哋講緊邊方面嘅利益衝突啦<br />\n但最基本你可以見到佢哋之前所有cover都係比eagle搶撚晒擺落自己channel<br />\n都係為咗build up今次嘅新歌hit rate<br />\n<br />\n同埋條友真係好撚嘔心<br />\n永遠淨係cap自己想見到嘅嘢 例如咩有台灣fans 然後又扮到好錫fans會寄俾台灣fans<br />\n又含沙射影話自己樂壇未來...<br />\n我唔否認佢係好努力 又或者有天份<br />\n但想型咪講囉 又要扮到由細個開始已經有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條友就係典型呢啲屎忽野 可能普通人睇會覺得冇咩 但識內阻佢真係知道晒佢想點 條友係典型仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMc雖然係串 但冇條友咁仆街 佢嗰種仆街係ian嗰種心術不正"}]}